      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "NORTH YAKIMA, June 21.-The\nalfalfa supply OF this valley will be\ncontrolled by a trust now in pro-\ncess of organization among the\nfarmers. No prices are quoted on\nthe new crop. The big commission\nmen are practically at the mercy of\nthe growers and will have to pay\nthe price asked If they handle the\nhay. The farmers have been com.\nPEELED to pay a higher wage scale\nfor helm this wear."
